## Customize flags given to the VM: https://www.erlang.org/doc/man/erl.html
## -mode/-name/-sname/-setcookie are configured via env vars, do not set them here

## M11 burrito-stdio fix: pass `-noinput` so Erlang's `prim_tty` /
## `:user` does NOT claim fd 0. pharos opens its own `{fd,0,0}` port
## from `pharos_stdin_ffi:read_line/1` for synchronous, unbuffered
## per-line stdin delivery. Without `-noinput` the driver fight
## emits a `driver_select stealing control of fd=0` error to fd 1
## that corrupts the MCP NDJSON stream.
-noinput
